00:01:50.010 --> 00:01:53.013 align:middle line:84%
And so I came fresh from
university and I studied a lot

00:01:53.013 --> 00:01:55.950 align:middle line:84%
about options and
portfolio management,

00:01:55.950 --> 00:01:58.519 align:middle line:84%
