to do with finance.

00:01:58.519 --> 00:02:00.454 align:middle line:90%
And then I started working.

00:02:00.454 --> 00:02:03.290 align:middle line:84%
On my first day I heard
my boss saying listen,

00:02:03.290 --> 00:02:07.027 align:middle line:84%
I want you to forget everything
you learned at the university.

00:02:07.027 --> 00:02:10.431 align:middle line:84%
I want you to be a blank page
for a moment, a clean sheet.

00:02:10.431 --> 00:02:11.765 align:middle line:90%
Yeah, forget everything.

00:02:11.765 --> 00:02:14.668 align:middle line:84%
There's only two things that
are important for a trader.

00:02:14.668 --> 00:02:17.738 align:middle line:84%
The first is a trader
doesn't have a big ego,

00:02:17.738 --> 00:02:21.542 align:middle line:84%
because if you have an ego
it shows in either fear;

00:02:21.542 --> 00:02:25.112 align:middle line:84%
being fearful or being too
big for your boots, you know.

00:02:25.112 --> 00:02:27.648 align:middle line:84%
You know the saying that you
feel so good about yourself

00:02:27.648 --> 00:02:30.451 align:middle line:90%
that you are like number one.

00:02:30.451 --> 00:02:35.089 align:middle line:84%
This is both ego and if you do
that as a trader you're going

00:02:35.089 --> 00:02:38.192 align:middle line:84%
to make mistakes and
you're going to lose money.

00:02:38.192 --> 00:02:40.026 align:middle line:84%
And the second lesson,
the second feature

00:02:40.026 --> 00:02:44.365 align:middle line:84%
of a good trader is that a good
trader is always in the moment.

00:02:44.365 --> 00:02:47.368 align:middle line:84%
It doesn't matter if
you just did your worst

00:02:47.368 --> 00:02:49.470 align:middle line:84%
or your best trade
ever in your life.

00:02:49.470 --> 00:02:50.404 align:middle line:90%
It doesn't matter.

00:02:50.404 --> 00:02:52.573 align:middle line:90%
There's only the trade to come.

00:02:52.573 --> 00:02:54.842 align:middle line:84%
So, this is the-- yeah,
it's really amazing

00:02:54.842 --> 00:02:58.245 align:middle line:84%
that you learn this on
the auction exchange.

00:02:58.245 --> 00:03:01.215 align:middle line:84%
You know your first lesson it's
very spiritual you could say.

00:03:01.215 --> 00:03:04.618 align:middle line:84%
