weight on what we think

00:03:21.602 --> 00:03:23.937 align:middle line:84%
and we give it too
much importance.

00:03:23.937 --> 00:03:25.606 align:middle line:90%
And I think that spirituality

00:03:25.606 --> 00:03:28.275 align:middle line:84%
in general is just
following your intuition.

00:03:28.275 --> 00:03:31.278 align:middle line:84%
And it doesn't really
matter if you're a banker

00:03:31.278 --> 00:03:33.714 align:middle line:90%
or a yoga teacher or a farmer.

00:03:33.714 --> 00:03:36.250 align:middle line:84%
If you follow your intuition
you're basically helping the

00:03:36.250 --> 00:03:37.918 align:middle line:90%
world further.

00:03:37.918 --> 00:03:39.553 align:middle line:84%
And I have to say
at the same time

00:03:39.553 --> 00:03:42.523 align:middle line:84%
