00:04:09.049 --> 00:04:09.817 align:middle line:90%
I mean what was that?

00:04:09.817 --> 00:04:10.718 align:middle line:90%
Was there a tipping point?

00:04:10.718 --> 00:04:11.785 align:middle line:90%
>> van der Vliet: Yeah.

00:04:11.785 --> 00:04:13.120 align:middle line:84%
Well, actually there
was a certain moment

00:04:13.120 --> 00:04:16.557 align:middle line:84%
in my trading period
where I lost all my money

00:04:16.557 --> 00:04:17.925 align:middle line:90%
in six months' time.

00:04:17.925 --> 00:04:22.029 align:middle line:84%
So, I had 600,000 Euros and I
lost it in six months' time.

00:04:22.029 --> 00:04:25.399 align:middle line:84%
And this was my six
months of being in fear.

00:04:25.399 --> 00:04:28.836 align:middle line:84%
I completely stepped
into my fear.

00:04:28.836 --> 00:04:34.141 align:middle line:84%
And it started with worries of
losing all the money that I had.

00:04:34.141 --> 00:04:38.178 align:middle line:84%
