that fear and I only saw

00:04:38.178 --> 00:04:43.450 align:middle line:84%
that, I didn't sleep well and
I-- it was a terrible period.

00:04:43.450 --> 00:04:45.586 align:middle line:90%
But, because of that period

00:04:45.586 --> 00:04:48.756 align:middle line:84%
after six months
I lost everything

00:04:48.756 --> 00:04:51.925 align:middle line:84%
and the funny thing was that
the day after I lost everything

00:04:51.925 --> 00:04:53.660 align:middle line:84%
so you have to imagine
that six months

00:04:53.660 --> 00:04:56.764 align:middle line:84%
of almost no sleep
and just pure panic.

00:04:56.764 --> 00:05:00.167 align:middle line:84%
And after six months
I lost everything

00:05:00.167 --> 00:05:02.436 align:middle line:90%
and I also lost my fear.

00:05:02.436 --> 00:05:04.171 align:middle line:90%
So, I was actually relieved

00:05:04.171 --> 00:05:06.240 align:middle line:84%
because it was all
gone including my fear.

00:05:06.240 --> 00:05:10.344 align:middle line:84%
