fearful of losing something

00:05:10.344 --> 00:05:14.581 align:middle line:84%
for example, is actually worse
than losing that something is.

00:05:14.581 --> 00:05:15.883 align:middle line:90%
>> Lilou: Yeah.

00:05:15.883 --> 00:05:19.887 align:middle line:84%
>> van der Vliet: So, this
was my true facing my fears.

00:05:19.887 --> 00:05:24.858 align:middle line:84%
