for other people--

00:38:36.348 --> 00:38:37.682 align:middle line:90%
>> Lilou: Mmm.

00:38:37.682 --> 00:38:39.618 align:middle line:84%
>> van der Vliet: Because
you're being straight basically.

00:38:39.618 --> 00:38:40.452 align:middle line:90%
>> Lilou: Mmm.

00:38:40.452 --> 00:38:41.386 align:middle line:90%
>> van der Vliet: If you start--

