This is what I'm really good
at, just talking to people.

00:39:57.696 --> 00:39:58.497 align:middle line:90%
>> Lilou: Yeah.

00:39:58.497 --> 00:39:59.531 align:middle line:90%
>> van der Vliet: And that--

