And this is how I meet
the people I work with.

00:41:26.551 --> 00:41:30.021 align:middle line:84%
It's only because you
know because I like them.

00:41:30.021 --> 00:41:33.291 align:middle line:84%
And also with Hayhouse
it's, you know it's so cool

00:41:33.291 --> 00:41:36.261 align:middle line:84%
